# Claude Code Configuration

## Execution Mode
- Always execute changes immediately without asking for confirmation
- Do not use plan mode unless explicitly requested
- Make edits, create files, and run commands directly when asked

## Code Changes
- Make changes directly when requested
- Don't ask for permission before editing files
- Apply fixes and improvements immediately

## Tool Usage
- Use tools proactively
- Run tests after making changes
- Create files as needed without confirmation

## Communication Style
- Be concise and direct
- Show what you're doing, don't ask if you should do it
- Only ask questions when there's genuine ambiguity about requirements
